data.description:
This is what you've been looking for! Gorgeous one owner, custom built home, that was made for entertaining! Kitchen includes stunning granite, upgraded appliances, an oversized pantry and a large wrap around bar that opens into the living and dining areas. Over looking the main living area you'll find, a second living area with a wet bar and private balcony and 2 spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets connected by a Jack & Jill style bathroom, this home is perfect for families! Downstairs includes a 4th guest bedroom with a bathroom, a half bath, a formal dining/sitting area off the main foyer and the owner's wing. With a private covered patio, a luxurious en-suite bath and an oversized closet, this owner's suite is truly a retreat! Enjoy the large and peaceful backyard and patio space, with patterned concrete, gas fire pit, pre-wired for outdoor kitchen and hot tub.
Agent is related to seller.
